Interface EnhancedAsynchACC

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AsynchACC, BulkAsynchACC, OrdinaryAsynchACC, RootACC, SpecificationAsynchACC, UniformAsynchACC
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EnhancedACC

    public interface EnhancedAsynchACC
extends AsynchACC, BulkAsynchACC, UniformAsynchACC
    Enhanced Asynchronous ACC. Can act both on the ordinary tuple space and on the specification tuple space. Bulk and uniform primitives are included.
    See Also:
    AsynchACC, BulkAsynchACC, UniformAsynchACC
